ğŸ“– Project Overview
The Weather Automation Tool (V2) is a Python-based application that automates the process of fetching real-time weather data for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API.
This version improves on V1 by integrating live API data, adding input handling, and displaying a clear, formatted weather report.
